com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.blob.models

Class ListBlobBlocksResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.blob.models.ListBlobBlocksResult

  • public class ListBlobBlocksResult
extends java.lang.Object
    A wrapper class for the response returned from a Blob Service REST API Get Block List operation. This is returned by calls to implementations of BlobContract.listBlobBlocks(String, String) and BlobContract.listBlobBlocks(String, String, ListBlobBlocksOptions).

    See the Get Block List documentation on MSDN for details of the underlying Blob Service REST API operation.

      • getLastModified

        public java.util.Date getLastModified()
        Gets the last modified time of the block blob. This value is returned only if the blob has committed blocks.

        Any operation that modifies the blob, including updates to the blob's metadata or properties, changes the last modified time of the blob. This value can be used in an access condition when updating or deleting a blob to prevent the client from modifying data that has been changed by another client.

        Returns:
        A Date containing the last modified time of the blob.

        This method is invoked by the API to set the value from the Blob Service REST API operation response returned by the server.
